Before any AUC / “underperformance” / architecture verdict on SignedKAN, HSiKAN, Bitcoin, Epinions, or Slashdot:

1. Read **`docs/RESULTS_DISCIPLINE.md`** and the cited files there (aggregate indexes, `joint_mix_5seed_2026_05_08.jsonl`, `phase8_bitcoin_5seed.json`, etc.).
2. Never merge **joint mix (~0.98 OTC)** with **phase-8 leanest (~0.85 OTC)** — different protocols; name which one.
